## Sections Explained

### Confluence Wiki Markup
- `h1.` - Level 1 heading
- `h2.` - Level 2 heading
- `h3.` - Level 3 heading
- `*bold*` - Bold text
- `||Header||` - Table header
- `|Cell|` - Table cell
- `{code}` - Code block
- `{code:json}` - Code block with syntax highlighting
- `!image.png!` - Inline image
- `!image.png|thumbnail!` - Thumbnail image
- `[Link text|URL]` - Hyperlink
- `----` - Horizontal rule
- `* item` - Bullet list
- `(/)` - Checkmark
- `{info}` - Info panel

